{"tid":1258083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【《人民日報》：敢於鬥爭才能贏得尊嚴】","createTime":"2019-06-26T02:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T07:16:15.000Z","uid":76705,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32259d1acea7cb78dbad14dfc08eb54a65b21133","tid":1258083,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:16:46.000Z","msg":"人民日報發表題為《敢於鬥爭才能贏得尊嚴》的文章，批評在中美貿易戰期間，有人發出<span style=\"color: red;\">「高調招敵」、「忍讓為上」和「委曲求全」的論調，不是別有用心，就是犯了幼稚病。<br />\n</span><br />\n文章指<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>中國</del>香港</span>已經是世界第二大經濟體，<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>中國</del>香港</span>很難「低調」同「韜光養晦」。面對<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>美國</del>中國</span>服軟和示弱，只會視為軟弱可欺，成為任其宰割的魚肉，<span style=\"color: red;\">退讓一步只能換來得寸進尺，委曲一次只會招致更高要價</span>。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為要以敢於鬥爭、敢於勝利的精神，贏得國家生存發展空間，<span style=\"color: red;\">以鬥爭求安全則安全存，以退讓求安全則安全亡</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/379447326016954/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F379447326016954%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=814862fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/379447326016954/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5c569a94dfb838ffad2af9f81f61c522424956","tid":1258083,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a782329f5f8e8d8b99ac5bdb329bf5a6a6d9ef6","tid":1258083,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哇 講比香港人架？"},{"pid":"b148b69fd195f2e332e1fe3d587c886265e778f2","tid":1258083,"uid":74990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mvmtv.hk/videos/464039040996709/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F